    },
    {
      "id": "factors-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1100,
      "y": 492,
      "width": 920,
      "height": 520,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f3e8ff",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 25,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1025,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1747612800000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "因子命令\n\n`tdx-stocks factors list`\n- 查看可用因子目录\n- `higher_is_better` 说明数值越大是否越强\n- 例如 `pct_rank_ret_20`、`rs_score`、`risk_score` 的排序语义不同\n\n`tdx-stocks factors describe <factor>`\n- 查看单个因子的定义、依赖、适用范围和排序方向\n- 适合确认某个字段是横截面因子、风险因子还是质量 flag\n\n`tdx-stocks factors schema`\n- 查看当前数据集暴露的字段\n- 包括 `factors` / `factors_xsec` / `factors_quality` / `factor_full`\n- 如果 `factor_full` 里某列是 `NULL`，通常说明当前版本数据还没生成该列\n\n`tdx-stocks factors rank <factor> --as-of latest --limit 50`\n- 按指定日期做横截面排名\n- 强弱类按降序；风险类、flag 类按升序\n- 百分位类已保证“数值越大越强”",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "因子命令\n\n`tdx-stocks factors list`\n- 查看可用因子目录\n- `higher_is_better` 说明数值越大是否越强\n- 例如 `pct_rank_ret_20`、`rs_score`、`risk_score` 的排序语义不同\n\n`tdx-stocks factors describe <factor>`\n- 查看单个因子的定义、依赖、适用范围和排序方向\n- 适合确认某个字段是横截面因子、风险因子还是质量 flag\n\n`tdx-stocks factors schema`\n- 查看当前数据集暴露的字段\n- 包括 `factors` / `factors_xsec` / `factors_quality` / `factor_full`\n- 如果 `factor_full` 里某列是 `NULL`，通常说明当前版本数据还没生成该列\n\n`tdx-stocks factors rank <factor> --as-of latest --limit 50`\n- 按指定日期做横截面排名\n- 强弱类按降序；风险类、flag 类按升序\n- 百分位类已保证“数值越大越强”",
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "baseline": 22
    },

    {
