    },
    {
      "id": "strategy-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2110,
      "y": 492,
      "width": 1020,
      "height": 520,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#fef3c7",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 27,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1027,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1747612800000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "策略命令\n\n`tdx-stocks strategy list`\n- 查看 preset、别名和策略说明\n\n`tdx-stocks strategy run <preset>`\n- 生成策略报告\n- `--save`: 保存到 `Database/reports/strategies/...`\n- `--as-of`: 指定观察日，默认最新交易日\n- `--limit`: 取前 N 条候选\n- `--min-score`: 最低得分阈值\n- `--min-amount-ma20`: 最低流动性阈值\n- `--candidate-type`: `strong_trend` / `breakout_watch` / `pullback_watch`\n- `--include-excluded`: 同时返回被排除样本\n- `--show-excluded-limit`: 控制排除样本数\n- `--explain-symbol`: 解释单只股票\n- `--output` / `--to`: 输出到文件，`--output` 为主推\n\n`strategy reports list/show`\n- 查看保存记录与单次报告\n- 需要 `--config` 指定数据库根目录\n\n`strategy compare / consensus`\n- `compare` 看策略重叠和独有股票\n- `consensus` 看多策略共振\n\n`strategy backtest / tune / analyze-*`\n- `backtest`: 滚动 T+1 信号回测\n- `tune`: 参数扫描\n- `analyze-forward-returns`: 看入选后未来 N 日收益\n- `analyze-risk-tags`: 看风险标签后收益\n- `backtest-consensus`: 多策略共振回测",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "策略命令\n\n`tdx-stocks strategy list`\n- 查看 preset、别名和策略说明\n\n`tdx-stocks strategy run <preset>`\n- 生成策略报告\n- `--save`: 保存到 `Database/reports/strategies/...`\n- `--as-of`: 指定观察日，默认最新交易日\n- `--limit`: 取前 N 条候选\n- `--min-score`: 最低得分阈值\n- `--min-amount-ma20`: 最低流动性阈值\n- `--candidate-type`: `strong_trend` / `breakout_watch` / `pullback_watch`\n- `--include-excluded`: 同时返回被排除样本\n- `--show-excluded-limit`: 控制排除样本数\n- `--explain-symbol`: 解释单只股票\n- `--output` / `--to`: 输出到文件，`--output` 为主推\n\n`strategy reports list/show`\n- 查看保存记录与单次报告\n- 需要 `--config` 指定数据库根目录\n\n`strategy compare / consensus`\n- `compare` 看策略重叠和独有股票\n- `consensus` 看多策略共振\n\n`strategy backtest / tune / analyze-*`\n- `backtest`: 滚动 T+1 信号回测\n- `tune`: 参数扫描\n- `analyze-forward-returns`: 看入选后未来 N 日收益\n- `analyze-risk-tags`: 看风险标签后收益\n- `backtest-consensus`: 多策略共振回测",
      "lineHeight": 1.18,
      "baseline": 22
    },

