      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 31,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1031,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1747612800000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "报告与落盘\n\n策略报告路径\n- `Database/reports/strategies/latest/<strategy>.json`\n- `Database/reports/strategies/by_date/<YYYY-MM-DD>/<strategy>.json`\n- `Database/reports/strategies/by_run_id/<run_id>/<strategy>.json`\n- 保存采用临时文件 + 原子替换，避免半个 JSON 文件\n\n策略报告字段\n- `schema_version`、`app_version`、`strategy_name`\n- `as_of`、`generated_at`、`data_run_id`、`factor_version`\n- `params`、`candidate_count`、`excluded_count`\n- `candidates`、`excluded_summary`、`risk_summary`、`diagnostics`\n\n因子与质量报告\n- `factor_catalog_report.json`\n- `data_quality_report.json`\n- `factor_quality_report.json`\n\n使用建议\n- `strategy reports list` 先看保存记录\n- `strategy reports show` 查看单个报告\n- `compare` / `consensus` 适合横向分析\n- `backtest` / `tune` 适合研究稳定性",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "报告与落盘\n\n策略报告路径\n- `Database/reports/strategies/latest/<strategy>.json`\n- `Database/reports/strategies/by_date/<YYYY-MM-DD>/<strategy>.json`\n- `Database/reports/strategies/by_run_id/<run_id>/<strategy>.json`\n- 保存采用临时文件 + 原子替换，避免半个 JSON 文件\n\n策略报告字段\n- `schema_version`、`app_version`、`strategy_name`\n- `as_of`、`generated_at`、`data_run_id`、`factor_version`\n- `params`、`candidate_count`、`excluded_count`\n- `candidates`、`excluded_summary`、`risk_summary`、`diagnostics`\n\n因子与质量报告\n- `factor_catalog_report.json`\n- `data_quality_report.json`\n- `factor_quality_report.json`\n\n使用建议\n- `strategy reports list` 先看保存记录\n- `strategy reports show` 查看单个报告\n- `compare` / `consensus` 适合横向分析\n- `backtest` / `tune` 适合研究稳定性",
      "lineHeight": 1.18,
      "baseline": 22
    },

