      "updated": 1747612800000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "常用示例\n\n`tdx-stocks data status`  |  `tdx-stocks data quality-report`  |  `tdx-stocks factors rank rs_score --as-of latest --limit 20`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy run trend_strength --as-of 2026-05-15 --limit 10 --min-amount-ma20 100000000 --save`\n`tdx-stocks strategy reports list`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy reports show trend-strength --as-of 2026-05-15`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy compare --as-of latest --strategies trend-strength,low-vol-breakout`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy consensus --as-of latest --min-hit 2`\n`tdx-stocks strategy backtest trend-strength --from 2022-01-01 --to 2024-12-31 --top 20 --hold-days 5`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy tune trend-strength --from 2022-01-01 --to 2024-12-31 --min-score 55,60,65 --top 10,20,30 --hold-days 5,10,20`",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "常用示例\n\n`tdx-stocks data status`  |  `tdx-stocks data quality-report`  |  `tdx-stocks factors rank rs_score --as-of latest --limit 20`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy run trend_strength --as-of 2026-05-15 --limit 10 --min-amount-ma20 100000000 --save`\n`tdx-stocks strategy reports list`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy reports show trend-strength --as-of 2026-05-15`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy compare --as-of latest --strategies trend-strength,low-vol-breakout`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy consensus --as-of latest --min-hit 2`\n`tdx-stocks strategy backtest trend-strength --from 2022-01-01 --to 2024-12-31 --top 20 --hold-days 5`  |  `tdx-stocks strategy tune trend-strength --from 2022-01-01 --to 2024-12-31 --min-score 55,60,65 --top 10,20,30 --hold-days 5,10,20`",
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "baseline": 25
    },

